Figures 283–286:
Left hemispermatophore of 

Reddyanus basilicus

from locality 15CR. External (283), dorsal (284), internal (285) and ventral (286) views. Scale bar: 500 µm. Abbreviations: 
bl
, basal lobe; 
f
, flagellum; 
ml
, median lobe; 
mlc
